  <h2>Why are email alerts important in Wazuh?</h2>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Fast response</strong>: The security team gets immediate notifications without constantly checking the dashboard</li>
    <li><strong>Automatic escalation</strong>: You can route alerts to different people depending on the type of incident</li>
    <li><strong>Documentary evidence</strong>: Emails act as a secondary record for audits</li>
    <li><strong>24/7 availability</strong>: Alerts arrive even when no one is actively monitoring</li>
    <li><strong>Regulatory compliance</strong>: Demonstrates that an operational incident notification system exists</li>
  </ul>

